    "content" : "1967, 13 window deluxe LHD walk-through. MOT’d to 03/08/16. Only selling due to low use and the need for space. This bus is a joy to own (one of the best he’s ever driven according to Paul at the Bus and Beetle Depot Nottingham). This was originally an American vehicle imported to the UK in 2007, hence the left hand drive! \n<br>\n<br>Patinated OG Velvet Green body (over-layered with a clear protective lacquer) re-sprayed and (expertly) matted down Alaska White roof. Garaged throughout its ownership. Very clean chassis. £28k ono (including accessories outlined below).\n<br>\n<br>￼￼\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12173&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12173&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010266.JPG\" title=\"P1010266.JPG (74.79 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>￼\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12175&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12175&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010267.JPG\" title=\"P1010267.JPG (85.83 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12176&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12176&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010268.JPG\" title=\"P1010268.JPG (71.47 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>Many additions and adaptations including:\n<br>\n<br>• \n<span style=\"font-weight: bold\">ENGINE: </span>\n<br>o 1641cc twin port engine \n<br>o twin Solex carbs.\n<br>o Recent replacement fuel lines.\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12177&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12177&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010269.JPG\" title=\"P1010269.JPG (62.27 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>o CSP gear shifter.\n<br>o New starter motor (2014).\n<br>• \n<span style=\"font-weight: bold\">SUSPENSION &amp; Running gear: </span>\n<br>o IRS with adjustable spring plates front and rear.\n<br>o Narrowed front beams.\n<br>o CSP front disc brakes.\n<br>o Unusual (but vey much in keeping) American Racing alloy wheels with locking wheel nuts.\n<br>• (Wolfsburg-West) front and (CE) rear safari-windows. New (Butty) seals added in 2012.\n<br>• Jail-bars on rear side and rear safari.\n<br>• Refurbished gear box and new clutch (July 2011).\n<br>• \n<span style=\"font-weight: bold\">Interior:</span> Full interior restoration in 2009 including solid oak cabinets, rock and roll bed, fold away oak table, pistachio with racing green striped upholstery, new rubberised floor covering with fitted/removable carpets and new unmarked headliner by Vaughn and Tim at Custom Classic and Retro. (more pictures on their website: \n<!-- m -->\n<a class=\"postlink\" href=\"http://www.customclassicretro.co.uk/Oak%20Camper%20Interior.html\">http://www.customclassicretro.co.uk/Oak ... erior.html</a>\n<!-- m -->)\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12178&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12178&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010272.JPG\" title=\"P1010272.JPG (58.68 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12179&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12179&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010271.JPG\" title=\"P1010271.JPG (92 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>\n<br>\n<br>• Interior 12v hook up for fridge under buddy seat.\n<br>• 12v LED lighting.\n<br>• Leisure battery with 240v hook up.\n<br>• Front screen cover and full bus cover included.\n<br>• \n<span style=\"font-weight: bold\">Safety/Security: </span>\n<br>o Engine bay: automatic Firetec Fire extinguisher with chafe guard (as sold by VW Jim on SSVC).\n<br>o Battery Isolator switch with removable ‘key’.\n<br>• Regular services and upkeep by Bus and Beetle depot with plenty of paperwork including work receipts, MOTs and USA/UK importation/restoration paperwork.\n<br>\n<br>Accessories included in the price:\n<br>Khyam Motordome awning.\n<br>silver screen for windscreen\n<br>full bus cover\n<br>Camping Gaz bottle\n<br>(other camping accessories negotiable)\n<br>\n<br>Bad bits:\n<br>• Small dent and scratch (touched up) in rear of the roof due to a fight with the garage door (doh!)\n<br>• Historic but ‘in keeping’ crease in rear passenger door (see bottom of LH door in the photo below) Fits with the general patination but want to be upfront about its foibles!\n<div class=\"inline-attachment\"> \n <dl class=\"thumbnail\"> \n  <dt>\n   <a href=\"./download/file.php?id=12174&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5&amp;mode=view\"><img src=\"./download/file.php?id=12174&amp;t=1&amp;sid=96cfea19623984d38329127f8b82fde5\" class=\"postimage\" alt=\"P1010265.JPG\" title=\"P1010265.JPG (85.7 KiB) Viewed 3850 times\"></a>\n  </dt> \n </dl> \n</div>",
